### version
mix phoenix.new --version
mix phx.new --version



### using different versions
# phoenix is just a project dependancy
# if you specify "~> 1.1.0" in that project only >= 1.1.0 && < 1.2.0 will be used.
# One thing to note is that when you “install” phoenix,
# you only install the phx.new (or phoenix.new) task.
# Everything else is packaged in the dependency you have in your project

# uninstall an older version of phoenix
mix archive.uninstall phoenix_new-1.2.5




### new project
mix phx.new <name>
mix phoenix.new <project name>




### start server
mix phoenix.server
mix phx.server




